<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2382] statistics component not fsynced</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2382</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The statistics file is prone to getting lost during a hard reset since it is not fsynced like the other sstable components.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12502344">CASSANDRA-2382</key>
            <summary>statistics component not fsynced</summary>
